import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";

const addresses = ["Phòng khách", "Phòng ngủ", "Nhà bếp", "Phòng làm việc"];

function DeviceManager({ user, onDevicesUpdate }) {
const [devices, setDevices] = useState([]);

const [form, setForm] = useState({
DEVICE_NAME: "",
ADDRESS: addresses[0],
STATUS: "On",
});

// Load devices từ server khi mount hoặc user thay đổi
useEffect(() => {
const fetchDevices = async () => {
if (!user?.USER_ID) return;
try {
const res = await fetch(
`http://localhost:5000/api/devices/user/${user.USER_ID}`
);
const data = await res.json();
const colored = data.map((d) => ({
...d,
color: d.color || "#" + Math.floor(Math.random() * 16777215).toString(16),
}));
setDevices(colored);
if (onDevicesUpdate) onDevicesUpdate(colored);
} catch (err) {
console.error(err);
}
};
fetchDevices();
}, [user, onDevicesUpdate]);

// Thêm thiết bị
const handleAdd = async () => {
if (!form.DEVICE_NAME.trim()) {
alert("Nhập Tên thiết bị");
return;
}

``
const newDevicePayload = {
  DEVICE_NAME: form.DEVICE_NAME,
  ADDRESS: form.ADDRESS,
  STATUS: form.STATUS,
  USER_ID: user?.USER_ID,
};

try {
  const res = await fetch("http://localhost:5000/api/devices", {
    method: "POST",
    headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },
    body: JSON.stringify(newDevicePayload),
  });
  const newDevice = await res.json();
  newDevice.color =
    "#" + Math.floor(Math.random() * 16777215).toString(16);

  const updatedDevices = [...devices, newDevice];
  setDevices(updatedDevices);
  if (onDevicesUpdate) onDevicesUpdate(updatedDevices);

  setForm({ DEVICE_NAME: "", ADDRESS: addresses[0], STATUS: "On" });
} catch (err) {
  console.error(err);
  alert("Thêm device thất bại");
}


};

return (
<div style={{ padding: 16, display: "flex", flexDirection: "column", gap: 24 }}>
{/* Form thêm thiết bị */}
<div
style={{
backgroundColor: "#fff",
padding: 26,
borderRadius: 26,
boxShadow: "0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)",
maxWidth: 2000,
}}
> <h3>Thêm thiết bị mới</h3>
<input
type="text"
placeholder="Tên thiết bị"
value={form.DEVICE_NAME}
onChange={(e) => setForm({ ...form, DEVICE_NAME: e.target.value })}
style={{ width: "100%", marginBottom: 12, padding: 8, borderRadius: 6, border: "1px solid #ccc" }}
/>
<select
value={form.ADDRESS}
onChange={(e) => setForm({ ...form, ADDRESS: e.target.value })}
style={{ width: "100%", marginBottom: 12, padding: 8, borderRadius: 6, border: "1px solid #ccc" }}
>
{addresses.map((a) => ( <option key={a}>{a}</option>
))} </select>
<select
value={form.STATUS}
onChange={(e) => setForm({ ...form, STATUS: e.target.value })}
style={{ width: "100%", marginBottom: 12, padding: 8, borderRadius: 6, border: "1px solid #ccc" }}
> <option>On</option> <option>Off</option> </select>
<button
onClick={handleAdd}
style={{
width: "100%",
padding: 10,
borderRadius: 6,
border: "none",
backgroundColor: "#4caf50",
color: "#fff",
fontWeight: "bold",
cursor: "pointer",
}}
>
Thêm thiết bị </button> </div>


  {/* Danh sách thiết bị */}
  <div style={{ display: "flex", flexWrap: "wrap", gap: 16 }}>
    {devices.map((d) => (
      <div
        key={d.DEVICE_ID}
        style={{
          flex: "1 1 220px",
          backgroundColor: "#fff",
          borderRadius: 12,
          boxShadow: "0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)",
          padding: 16,
          borderLeft: `6px solid ${d.color}`,
          transition: "transform 0.2s",
        }}
        onMouseEnter={(e) => (e.currentTarget.style.transform = "scale(1.03)")}
        onMouseLeave={(e) => (e.currentTarget.style.transform = "scale(1)")}
      >
        <h4>{d.DEVICE_NAME}</h4>
        <p><strong>Địa chỉ:</strong> {d.ADDRESS}</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Status:</strong>{" "}
          <span style={{ color: d.STATUS === "On" ? "#4caf50" : "#f44336" }}>
            {d.STATUS}
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>


);
}

export default DeviceManager;
